SUMMARY:Cloud Native AI + Kubeflow Day | Sponsored Keynote: The 2026 Infrastructure\, Operations\, and Cloud Services Agenda: Scaling Agentic AI with Platform Engineering - Kevin Cochrane\, Vultr
DESCRIPTION:2026 is the year heads of IOCS need to embrace AI\, innovate\, and move faster - all while cutting costs\, scaling globally\, and safeguarding the business against security and compliance risks. &nbsp\;For 2026\, heads of IOCS need a simple\, straightforward path to deliver core platform services to their software development and data scientist teams. &nbsp\;To deliver platform services\, heads of IOCs need their platform engineering team to deliver the pre-tested development environments\, models\, and hardened infrastructure templates to connect data pipelines with GPU customers and scale up and scale down resources on-demand. &nbsp\;In this session\, learn how Platform Engineers can take charge of accelerating enterprise AI infrastructure and transforming IOCS.
CATEGORIES:CLOUD NATIVE AI + KUBEFLOW DAY
LOCATION:Hall 7 | Room B\, Amsterdam\, Netherlands
