SUMMARY:Platform Engineering Day l Sponsored Keynote: Why Kubernetes Node OS Still Shapes Performance\, Security\, and Scale - Naadir Jeewa\, Broadcom
DESCRIPTION:Containers abstract applications\, but the Kubernetes node OS still plays a critical role. Kernel behavior\, update strategies\, and OS lifecycle alignment influence cluster stability\, security posture\, and upgrade confidence. This talk explores why platform engineers should treat the node OS as part of the Kubernetes platform contract\, and how thoughtful OS choices help teams operate reliable\, scalable clusters across diverse environments.
CATEGORIES:PLATFORM ENGINEERING DAY
LOCATION:Hall 8 | Room F\, Amsterdam\, Netherlands
