SUMMARY:BackstageCon | Sponsored Keynote - AI Can't Use Data it Doesn't Have - David Tuite\, Roadie
DESCRIPTION:Everyone and their dog wants AI to interface with Backstage. Unfortunately\, we've all forgotten the most important step... collecting the data that the AI needs for context in Backstage in the first place. Let's examine a simple AI agent and see what it takes for our Backstage catalog to be up to the task.
CATEGORIES:BACKSTAGECON
LOCATION:Hall 8 | Room E\, Amsterdam\, Netherlands
