SUMMARY:BackstageCon | Sponsored Keynote - Your Backstage\, Our Grunt Work: Migrating to Spotify Portal Without Pausing Your Roadmap - Joe Combopiano\, Spotify
DESCRIPTION:You adopted Backstage to accelerate your developers\, but somewhere along the way your platform team became full-time infrastructure maintainers — wrangling upgrades\, patching security issues\, and absorbing breaking changes. Spotify Portal is the SaaS\, Spotify-managed edition of Backstage\, built by the same engineers who created and open-sourced it. In this talk\, we'll walk through what a real migration looks like\, who owns what\, and how your team keeps full control of plugins\, data\, and integrations without carrying the operational burden. We'll also preview the capabilities Portal unlocks once you're migrated — from AI-powered developer tools to scorecards\, feature flags\, and executive-level DevEx insights — the same tools Spotify uses internally\, now available to you. You'll leave with a clear picture of how to stop keeping the lights on and start building what's next.
CATEGORIES:BACKSTAGECON
LOCATION:Hall 8 | Room E\, Amsterdam\, Netherlands
SEQUENCE:0
UID:576c789259e2090b2e6a29bb479dc8cb
