DTSTART:20260323T091000Z
DTEND:20260323T091500Z
SUMMARY:FluxCon | Sponsored Keynote: Agentic GitOps: Evolving Enterprise Delivery - Andy Martin\, ControlPlane
DESCRIPTION:Ever had drift\, outages\, unclear blast radius\, slow troubleshooting across many clusters and teams? Massive scale deployments are not immune to these headaches.In a pragmatic two-step evolution for the Flux ecosystem\, from MCP-enabled AI assistance to agentic operations\, ControlPlane has laid a solid\, secure foundation for Enterprise teams to adopt safely and quickly.We introduce the vision behind Enterprise for Flux’s MCP\, transforming GitOps context into a reliable\, robust interface that AI tools and agents can query\, without having to infer the live state of the cluster fleet.
CATEGORIES:FLUXCON
LOCATION:Elicium 1\, Amsterdam\, Netherlands
SEQUENCE:0
UID:2693b428c93b39a324f52b3c202db486
URL:http://colocatedeventseu2026.sched.com/event/2693b428c93b39a324f52b3c202db486
