SUMMARY:Platform Engineering Day l Sponsored Keynote - Rebuilding Platforms for the ADLC - Justin Reock\, DX
DESCRIPTION:As we transition from the "Year of Agents" into the "Year of AI Orchestration\,” the mandate for Platform Engineering is shifting. It is no longer enough to manage CI/CD pipelines and container &nbsp\;clusters\, the new focus is the ADLC (AI Development Life Cycle). Based on emerging trends in the enterprise\, this lightning talk explores how platform teams are evolving from infrastructure stewards into architects of centralized AI hubs.
CATEGORIES:PLATFORM ENGINEERING DAY
LOCATION:Hall 8 | Room F\, Amsterdam\, Netherlands
