SUMMARY:⚡Lightning Talk: Unikernels Vs Containers Vs VMs - Ram Iyengar\, Linux Foundation
DESCRIPTION:This is a short talk that presents a multi-dimensional view of the various options available for cloud compute today. We live in a remarkable time. Because the number of options available to operators to run applications in the cloud is unprecedented.\nUnikernels\, lightweight VMs (think Firecracker\, Hyperlight)\, Containers\, Virtual Machines - the list goes on. What makes each of these unique? What makes them a good choice? What are ways to use\, misuse\, and abuse these?\nAnswers to these questions make up this talk.
CATEGORIES:KUBERNETES ON EDGE DAY
LOCATION:Emerald Room\, Amsterdam\, Netherlands
