DTSTAMP:20260321T190205Z
DTSTART:20260323T131000Z
DTEND:20260323T133500Z
SUMMARY:Packaging OpenTofu in pkgsrc - Leonardo Taccari\, The NetBSD Foundation
DESCRIPTION:Have you ever wondered how OpenTofu and OpenTofu providers can be packaged in a package system? \n \nIn this talk we will explore how OpenTofu and OpenTofu providers are packaged in pkgsrc\, the NetBSD package system that also supports several other Unix-like operating systems. \n \nWe will also see challenges on packaging it together with older Terraform and Terraform providers in order to permit a full migration from Terraform 0.12.x to latest OpenTofu.
CATEGORIES:OPENTOFU DAY
LOCATION:Emerald Room\, Amsterdam\, Netherlands
SEQUENCE:0
UID:254f83e589fb3e9a5b7e3f0c889c324f
URL:http://colocatedeventseu2026.sched.com/event/254f83e589fb3e9a5b7e3f0c889c324f
