DTSTAMP:20260321T190205Z
DTSTART:20260323T135000Z
DTEND:20260323T135500Z
SUMMARY:Agentics Day: MCP + Agents | Sponsored Keynote: Day-2 Ready: Bringing agentic pilots to production - Idit Levine & Keith Babo\, Solo.io
DESCRIPTION:While many organizations have seen initial success deploying LLM-integrated chatbots and agentic IDEs into internal or external production\, the vast majority of agentic projects are still stuck in day 1 pilots with no clear path to production. This talk will share best practice patterns and architectures for agentic infrastructure in use across the agentgateway\, kagent\, and agentregistry communities to help you bring your agentic pilots to day 2 and beyond.
CATEGORIES:AGENTICS DAY: MCP + AGENTS
LOCATION:Hall 7 | Room A\, Amsterdam\, Netherlands
