SUMMARY:Is AIOps the Future of Operations? Real Use Cases From the Trenches - Iveri Prangishvili & Danilo Banjac\, Adobe
DESCRIPTION:This session presents real-world AIOps use cases at Adobe\, demonstrating how Agentic workflows can automate on-call tasks\, streamline issue diagnosis and drive continuous improvement. Attendees will gain practical insights into building autonomous agents for operational space\, leveraging AIOps for scaling operations and reducing manual effort.
CATEGORIES:AGENTICS DAY: MCP + AGENTS
