DTSTAMP:20260321T190205Z
DTSTART:20260323T160000Z
DTEND:20260323T161000Z
SUMMARY:⚡Lightning Talk: Using Argo Workflows at Petabyte Scale: From CI To Data-Processing Pipelines - Arya Soni\, Exocode Technologies Private Limited
DESCRIPTION:We'll show you how we set up and ran Argo Workflows for processing large amounts of data. We'll talk about how we split up jobs\, chose between DAG and step templates\, used resource throttling\, measured job throughput and cost metrics\, used retry and back-off strategies\, and connected with Prometheus and Grafana for SLO monitoring. Finally\, we’ll share practical tips for teams transitioning from simple CI/CD pipelines to full-blown petabyte-scale workflows.
CATEGORIES:ARGOCON
LOCATION:Auditorium\, Amsterdam\, Netherlands
