SUMMARY:⚡Lightning Talk: The Platform's Workshop: Forging Our Perfect Dev Portal With Custom Backstage Plugins - Yogesh Sardana\, Cloud Researcher & Leader
DESCRIPTION:Backstage provides an incredible foundation for a developer portal\, but what happens when your company's unique tools and workflows don't fit the off-the-shelf plugins? Do you compromise your process or live with a fragmented experience? In this session\, I'll walk through a third option\, i.e. building our ownThis lightning talk dives into the world of custom Backstage plugin development. I'll show you how I went beyond the standard catalog\, writing "wrapper" plugins to bring experimental CLIs and bespoke APIs directly into the Backstage UI. You'll see how I transformed complex\, command-line-only operations into intuitive\, self-service actions\, creating a developer portal that is truly tailor-made for engineers.
CATEGORIES:BACKSTAGECON
LOCATION:Hall 8 | Room E\, Amsterdam\, Netherlands
SEQUENCE:0
