SUMMARY:⚡Lightning Talk: 5 Pitfalls of Building Developer Platforms - Jessica Andersson\, Jesande
DESCRIPTION:Everyone wants to build developer platforms\, but not everyone succeeds. What pitfalls can you avoid on your journey of empowering your developers? Join this talk to learn what signs to look for and what anti patterns to avoid when building internal develop platforms!
CATEGORIES:PLATFORM ENGINEERING DAY
LOCATION:Hall 8 | Room F\, Amsterdam\, Netherlands
